title: PA Rep. Brendan Boyle, Stimulus Stalemate
itunes:title: PA Rep. Brendan Boyle, Stimulus Stalemate
description:
Guests: Mario Parker, Bloomberg White House reporter, Michael Regan, Senior Editor and lead blogger for Bloomberg Markets Live, George Seay, CEO of Annandale Capital, Joel Rubin, Executive Director of the American Jewish Congress, and Rep. Brendan Boyle, a Democrat representing Pennsylvania's 2nd congressional district.
